quran[8{c,v,t}:
28,36,phir jab moose unn logon ke paas hamari khُli khُli nishanain le kar pouncha to unhon ne kaha ke yeh kuch nahi hai magar banawati jadugar aur yeh baatein to hum ne apne baap dada ke zamane mein kabhi sُnin hi nahi
28,37,"moose ne jawab diya"" mera rab uss shakhs ke haal se khoob waaqif hai jo is ki taraf se hadaayat le kar aaya hai aur wohi behtar jaanta hai ke aakhri injaam kis ka acha hona hai, haq yeh hai ke zalim kabhi Falah nahi paate """
28,38,"aur firaon ne kaha"" ae ahal darbaar mein to apne siwa tumahray kisi khuda ko nahi jaanta Haman , zara eenten pkwa kar mere liye aik onche imarat to banava, shayad ke is par charh kar mein moose ke khuda ko dekh sakun, mein to usay jhoota samjhta hon """
28,39,uss ne aur is ke lashkaron ne zameen mein baghair kisi haq ke apni barayi ka ghamand kya aur samjhay ke inhen kabhi hamari taraf palatna nahi hai
28,40,aakhir-kaar hum ne usay aur is ke lashkaron ko pakra aur samandar mein pheink diya ab dekh lau ke un zaalmon ka kaisa injaam howa
28,41,hum ne inhen jahannum ki taraf dawat dainay walay paish ro bana diya aur qayamat ke roz woh kahin se koi madad nah pa saken ge
28,42,hum ne iss duniya mein un ke peechay laanat laga di aur qayamat ke roz woh barri qabahat mein mubtala hon ge
28,43,"pichli naslon ko halaak karne ke baad hum ne moose ko kitaab ataa ki, logon ke liye basiraton ka samaan bana kar, taakay shayad log sabaq haasil karen"
